data.title: No Lash-Lash
data.meta_description: What it is: Sweed’s No.1 best-selling lash. These refined, delicate and beautiful lashes come in four different lengths to create the most natural-looking yet dramatic lash looks. Each no-lash lash is tapered at the end to mimic the appearance of a natural lash hair, making them totally imperceptible, with a light as air feeling.
data.text:
SHIPPING

Sweed offers free Standard Shipping on orders over $50 | €30 | £37. No code necessary. Free shipping will be applied at checkout and does not include duties. All of our products are shipped to you from Sweden via a secure, tracked shipping method.

All respective shipping fees are reflected on the checkout page.

RETURNS & REFUNDS If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you can easily return your Sweed product (s) within14 days of receiving the order. Please note that product(s) must be returned unused, undamaged and in its original cardboard outer packaging, which must remain sealed and thereby unopened. Please allow up to 14 days for your transaction to process. Your refund will be issued in the form of original payment, such as the credit card used for the order. Shipping and handling costs are not refundable.

EXCHANGES

Exchanges are not supported at this time - if you would like a product, please return your unwanted item and place a new order.

DO YOU DO ANY ANIMAL TESTING? We’re committed to being vegan and cruelty free. None of our products are tested on animals at any stage of product development, and we only work with vendors who uphold the same standards.

WHAT FORMS OF PAYMENT DO YOU ACCEPT?

We accept the following payment methods: Paypal, Visa, Mastercard and American Express.

WHERE CAN I SEE/ PURCHASE YOUR PRODUCTS IN PERSON? Please visit our Store Locator Page for a complete listing of all physical stores that carry our products.
